snippet.title: Cris Tales trailer - PC Gaming Show 2019
snippet.description:
Cris Tales is a stunning love letter to classic JRPGs that was first revealed at the PC Gaming Show. Though little is known, Cris Tales is expected to be out sometime next year.

Read more here: https://www.pcgamer.com/cris-tales-is-a-gorgeous-love-letter-to-classic-jrpgs/
